{"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"Waits for up to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"timeoutUs"},{"type":"text","text":" microseconds for "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"condition"},{"type":"text","text":" to become true"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"on "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"socket"},{"text":". If the condition is met, ","type":"text"},{"code":"true","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is returned.","type":"text"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"conditionTimedWait","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"condition","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"IOCondition","preciseIdentifier":"s:4GLib11IOConditionV","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"timeoutUs","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:glibconfig.h@T@gint64","text":"gint64","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"cancellable","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/CancellableRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO14CancellableRefV","text":"CancellableRef"},{"text":"? = nil) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"throws","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"code":"cancellable","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is cancelled before the condition is met, or if","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"timeoutUs"},{"type":"text","text":" (or the socket’s "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/